<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
     <meta charset="UTF-8">
     <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
     <title>Page Non Trouv√©e - Erreur 404 - Ndressilik</title>
     <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
     <style>
          body,
          html {
               height: 100%;
               margin: 0;
               font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
               background-color: #f0f7f4;
               display: flex;
               align-items: center;
               justify-content: center;
               color: #333;
               overflow: hidden;
          }

          .container {
               text-align: center;
               padding: 2rem;
               max-width: 600px;
               position: relative;
          }

          h1 {
               font-size: 3rem;
               margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
               color: #3FB1B0;
          }

          .error-code {
               font-size: 1.5rem;
               font-weight: 600;
               color: #FF6B6B;
               margin-bottom: 1rem;
          }

          p {
               font-size: 1.2rem;
               margin-bottom: 2rem;
               line-height: 1.6;
          }

          .btn {
               display: inline-block;
               padding: 12px 24px;
               background-color: #3FB1B0;
               color: white;
               text-decoration: none;
               border-radius: 30px;
               font-size: 1.1rem;
               font-weight: 600;
               transition: all 0.3s ease;
               box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
          }

          .btn:hover,
          .btn:focus {
               background-color: #2C7A7B;
               transform: translateY(-2px);
               box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
          }

          .dog-scene {
               width: 300px;
               height: 200px;
               margin: 0 auto 2rem;
               position: relative;
               overflow: hidden;
          }

          .dog {
               width: 100px;
               height: 60px;
               background-color: #A0522D;
               border-radius: 50px 50px 0 0;
               position: absolute;
               bottom: 20px;
               left: -100px;
               animation: runDog 4s linear infinite;
          }

          .dog::before {
               content: '';
               width: 60px;
               height: 60px;
               background-color: #A0522D;
               border-radius: 50%;
               position: absolute;
               top: -30px;
               left: 20px;
          }

          .dog::after {
               content: 'ü¶¥';
               font-size: 24px;
               position: absolute;
               top: -40px;
               right: -20px;
          }

          @keyframes runDog {
               0% {
                    left: -100px;
               }

               50% {
                    left: 300px;
               }

               50.01% {
                    left: -100px;
                    transform: scaleX(-1);
               }

               100% {
                    left: 300px;
                    transform: scaleX(-1);
               }
          }

          .hole {
               width: 60px;
               height: 30px;
               background-color: #8B4513;
               border-radius: 50%;
               position: absolute;
               bottom: 0;
               left: 50%;
               transform: translateX(-50%);
          }

          #fetch-button {
               background-color: #FF6B6B;
               margin-top: 1rem;
          }

          #fetch-button:hover,
          #fetch-button:focus {
               background-color: #e05252;
          }

          @media (max-width: 480px) {
               h1 {
                    font-size: 2.5rem;
               }

               .error-code {
                    font-size: 1.2rem;
               }

               p {
                    font-size: 1rem;
               }

               .dog-scene {
                    transform: scale(0.8);
               }
          }
     </style>
</head>

<body>
     <div class="container">
          <div class="dog-scene">
               <div class="dog"></div>
               <div class="hole"></div>
          </div>
          <h1>Oups ! Page Non Trouv√©e</h1>
          <p class="error-code">Erreur 404</p>
          <p>Il semble que notre chien ait enterr√© cette page quelque part dans le jardin. Nous allons lui apprendre √† ne pas faire √ßa !</p>
          <p>En attendant, pourquoi ne pas retourner √† l'accueil pour explorer d'autres parties de notre site ?</p>
          <a href="/" class="btn">Retourner √† l'accueil</a>
          <button id="fetch-button" class="btn">Rapporte, mon chien !</button>
     </div>

     <script>
          document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', (event) => {
               const container = document.querySelector('.container');
               const fetchButton = document.getElementById('fetch-button');
               const dog = document.querySelector('.dog');

               // Initial animation
               container.style.opacity = '0';
               container.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';
               container.style.transition = 'opacity 0.5s ease-out, transform 0.5s ease-out';

               setTimeout(() => {
                    container.style.opacity = '1';
                    container.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
               }, 100);

               fetchButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    dog.style.animationPlayState = 'paused';
                    setTimeout(() => {
                         dog.style.animationPlayState = 'running';
                    }, 1000);

                    fetchButton.disabled = true;
                    fetchButton.textContent = 'Bon chien !';
                    setTimeout(() => {
                         fetchButton.disabled = false;
                         fetchButton.textContent = 'Rapporte encore !';
                    }, 2000);
               });
          });
     </script>
</body>

</html>